      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see what you're saying about discourse. but it seems like a lot of people feel that the \"social justice\" side of this is actually just a way to enforce a specific set of political values on everyone else. basically, if you don't agree with the specific progressive framework being pushed, you're automatically cast as the bad guy. isnt it basically just a tool for political indoctrination at that point?",
